                        <!-- About Us -->
                        <p>Pethudl is a dedicated social media platform for pets and their people.  
                        Our mission is to connect pet lovers worldwide, offering a safe, fun and interactive space to share stories, showcase pets, and build lasting memories.</p>

                        <p>Our mission is simple — build a community where pets and their people can connect, share and celebrate the joy of companionship.</p>

                        <p>Our goal is to bring pet lovers together in one place to create life-long friendships and explore shining pet moments.  
